<div class="panel panel-default" id="credit-cards-exercise">
    <div class="panel-heading">
        <strong>Ember Component Exercise</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <p>
            Modify the existing <code>credit-card</code> component to meet the following criteria:
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>Update the <code>isExpired</code> function of the <code>credit-card.js</code> component to return <code>true</code> if the card is expired.</li>
            <li>Use CSS to update the border color of the card to be red if the card is expired, and green otherwise.</li>
        </ol>
        <h2>Results:</h2>
        <div class="credit-cards-container text-center">
            {{#each model as |card|}}
                {{credit-card card=card}}
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
